<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مَنْصُورٌ:</span> وَبَلَغَنِي <span class="c2">«أَنَّ أَبَا بَكْرٍ، وَعُمَرَ سَجَدَا سَجْدَةَ الشُّكْرِ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>